Myers, Courtney Boyd ed. (2009). The AI Report. Forbes June 2009
Serenko, Alexander. The development of an AI journal ranking based on the revealed preference approach (PDF). Journal of Informetrics. 2010, 4 (4): 447–459. doi:10.1016/j.joi.2010.04.001. 
